<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q60_v15" title="Q60_v15" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En un grupo de datos, la desviación de un dato se calcula como 
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>x</m:mi>
        <m:mo>−</m:mo>
        <m:mi>p</m:mi>
      </m:math>, donde <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> es el dato y <m:math><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:math> es el promedio de los datos del grupo.
    </p>
    <p>En una lista de reproducción se registran las duraciones, en minutos, de cinco canciones: 3,12; 3,06; 3,16; 3,22 y 3,14. El promedio de estas duraciones es 3,14.</p>
    <p>Si se calcula la desviación para cada una de estas cinco duraciones, ¿cuál sería la mediana de esas desviaciones?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">-0,02<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Las desviaciones son <m:math><m:mn>3,12</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3,14</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>-0,02</m:mn></m:math>, <m:math><m:mn>3,06</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3,14</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>-0,08</m:mn></m:math>, <m:math><m:mn>3,16</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3,14</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,02</m:mn></m:math>, <m:math><m:mn>3,22</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3,14</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,08</m:mn></m:math> y <m:math><m:mn>3,14</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3,14</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:math>. Al ordenarlas se obtiene <m:math><m:mn>-0,08</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>-0,02</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0,02</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0,08</m:mn></m:math>. La mediana es el tercer valor, y ese valor es <m:math><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mn>-0,02</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">0<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Las desviaciones son <m:math><m:mn>3,12</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3,14</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>-0,02</m:mn></m:math>, <m:math><m:mn>3,06</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3,14</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>-0,08</m:mn></m:math>, <m:math><m:mn>3,16</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3,14</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,02</m:mn></m:math>, <m:math><m:mn>3,22</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3,14</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,08</m:mn></m:math> y <m:math><m:mn>3,14</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3,14</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:math>. Ordenadas de menor a mayor quedan <m:math><m:mn>-0,08</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>-0,02</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0,02</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0,08</m:mn></m:math>. La mediana es el tercer valor, por lo tanto la respuesta es <m:math><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">0,02<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Las desviaciones calculadas son <m:math><m:mn>-0,02</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>-0,08</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0,02</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0,08</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:math>. Al ordenarlas de menor a mayor se obtiene <m:math><m:mn>-0,08</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>-0,02</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0,02</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0,08</m:mn></m:math>. La mediana de cinco datos ordenados es el tercer valor, y aquí el tercer valor es <m:math><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mn>0,02</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">0,08<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La desviación <m:math><m:mn>0,08</m:mn></m:math> aparece porque <m:math><m:mn>3,22</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3,14</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,08</m:mn></m:math>, pero la pregunta pide la mediana de todas las desviaciones. Al ordenarlas se obtiene <m:math><m:mn>-0,08</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>-0,02</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0,02</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0,08</m:mn></m:math>. La mediana es el tercer valor de esta lista ordenada, y ese valor es <m:math><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mn>0,08</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Calcular cada desviación</strong></p>
            <p>La desviación se obtiene restando el promedio <m:math><m:mi>p</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3,14</m:mn></m:math> a cada dato.</p>
            <p>Para <m:math><m:mn>3,12</m:mn></m:math>: <m:math><m:mn>3,12</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3,14</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>-0,02</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Para <m:math><m:mn>3,06</m:mn></m:math>: <m:math><m:mn>3,06</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3,14</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>-0,08</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Para <m:math><m:mn>3,16</m:mn></m:math>: <m:math><m:mn>3,16</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3,14</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,02</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Para <m:math><m:mn>3,22</m:mn></m:math>: <m:math><m:mn>3,22</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3,14</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,08</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Para <m:math><m:mn>3,14</m:mn></m:math>: <m:math><m:mn>3,14</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>3,14</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Escribir la lista de desviaciones</strong></p>
            <p>Las cinco desviaciones son: <m:math><m:mn>-0,02</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>-0,08</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0,02</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0,08</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Ordenar las desviaciones de menor a mayor</strong></p>
            <p>Ordenando, queda: <m:math><m:mn>-0,08</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>-0,02</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0,02</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>0,08</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Identificar la mediana</strong></p>
            <p>Como hay cinco datos, la mediana es el valor que queda en la posición central, es decir, el tercer valor de la lista ordenada.</p>
            <p>El tercer valor es <m:math><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La mediana de las desviaciones es <m:math><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:math>, por lo tanto la alternativa correcta es la <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>